Re: SimpleDB perl code for creating domain - CreateDomainSample.xml
I was able to resolve it. At least in my case I had accidentally uncommented both:

use Amazon::SimpleDB::Client; 
 my $service = Amazon::SimpleDB::Client->new($AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID, $AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY);


AND

use Amazon::SimpleDB::Mock;  
my $service = Amazon::SimpleDB::Mock->new;

But you should only uncomment one set. When keeping the comments to the latter, I was able to get the expected reponse per the documentation.

I'm responding to the inquiry for any poor lad who's been pulling there hair out for the last hour or so

